Q1. What is SAP ERP? 
SAP is an ERP software that integrates various business functions such as Finance, Procurement, Sales, Manufacturing, and Human Resources into a single system. 
It enables organizations to streamline processes, improve data consistency, and support business operations through a centralized platform. 
SAP Security is responsible for managing users, roles, and authorizations to ensure secure and compliant access to SAP systems.

